<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa Jesuh kong ka chim tuah, Theih ka duh ko. Jesuh mah-ka a um
 ahcun, Ka hal laimi, Lam pawng hmuhmi hna, Rili tuanbia, Bawi Jesuh
 konglam ka chim dih tuah.

[V2]
 Ngakchia a kehram an dir kong, Ka chim hmasa, A thluachuahnak ka cung
 a um, Hi ka ruah lai, Zaangfahnak bia-thlum, Velngeih tuannak, Khrih
 hmaipanh ah dawtnak thlam a leng.

[V3]
 Khuapi chung tiangin ka zulh lai, Ngakchia bu hna, Tum-hnah an hler
 tikah, kei zong, Ka hler ve lai, A thangthattu ah, &quot;Jesuh Bawipa,
 Hosanna,&quot; tiin ka sak ve lai.</lyrics>
<title>JESUH KONG KA CHIM TUAH CH115</title>
<hymn_number>115</hymn_number>
</song>